c: 46
v: 21
t: "And remember (Hood), the brother of a people called ´Aad´? He warned his folks who lived in (a place called) ´Aikah´. Other warners had gone by ahead of him, and had followed him (in that land). He said, \"Do not worship anyone except Allah! In fact, I am afraid that a torment of a tremendous day might strike you down"